00:48.950 --> 00:52.000
Get rid of him.
- Just seeing if he's got a purse.

00:54.570 --> 00:56.770
I'll show you my purse
if you show me yours.

01:04.599 --> 01:06.600
This is an ambush.

01:06.900 --> 01:09.400
You don't say.
- This is how it goes.

01:09.660 --> 01:12.945
There's poor people going hungry.
Tell us what you've got...

01:13.025 --> 01:15.425
be honest with us.
- And we take one tenth...

01:15.550 --> 01:17.900
so the poor can eat.
- Lie...

01:18.020 --> 01:21.000
or resist
- And we take it all.

01:21.570 --> 01:23.570
So what's it gonna be?

01:39.025 --> 01:41.800
Well, what have we got here?

01:42.400 --> 01:44.400
My babies.

01:44.875 --> 01:46.875
Get them.

02:01.450 --> 02:03.450
I don't wanna hurt you
- Oh, sure you was.

02:09.180 --> 02:11.180
I've got the girl.

02:12.175 --> 02:14.175
Time to disappear!

02:14.245 --> 02:17.251
My gang, this way!

02:18.200 --> 02:20.200
The woman you'll find.

02:37.530 --> 02:39.530
Where did they go?

02:40.050 --> 02:42.050
Gone to meet their Makers.

02:42.300 --> 02:44.650
Take me to Nottingham. Idiots.

03:00.550 --> 03:02.350
Come on.

03:07.050 --> 03:09.500
It worked well.
- That was nothing.

03:09.750 --> 03:14.000
Nothing?
Jesus. I love our camp!

